--nums (one per line, empty line to finish)
> █
--- frame 1 (-) ---
--nums (one per line, empty line to finish)
> -█
--- frame 2 (5) ---
--nums (one per line, empty line to finish)
> -5█
--- frame 3 (enter) ---
--nums=-5
--- frame 4 (initial) ---
--nums (one per line, empty line to finish)
> █
