--name: Your name.
> █
--- frame 1 (b) ---
--name: Your name.
> b█
--- frame 2 (o) ---
--name: Your name.
> bo█
--- frame 3 (b) ---
--name: Your name.
> bob█
--- frame 4 (enter) ---
--name bob
